      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"كَفَّارَةُ اَلضَّحِكِ أَنْ يَقُولَ: اَللَّهُمَّ لاَ تَمْقُتْنِي \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4328 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"The expiation for excessive laughter is to say, 'O Allah (swt), do not despise me.'\""
        ]
      }
